305
00:19:44,340 --> 00:19:46,670
Takže ma s nimi nehádž do jedného vreca!

306
00:19:46,840 --> 00:19:48,440
Usui?

307
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:53,000
Oh.. aspoň tak si to myslím ja...

308
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:55,640
No...
 Huh!

309
00:19:57,750 --> 00:20:00,380
