313
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:18,470
Je to ako to čo sa stalo mame.

314
00:20:19,370 --> 00:20:22,670
Takže keď upíri pijú krv...

315
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:26,980
Au.
 Anju?!

316
00:20:28,050 --> 00:20:30,380
To dievča...
Je to tvoja kamarátka?

317
00:20:30,450 --> 00:20:33,720
To je moja sestra, Anju.
 Sestra?

318
00:20:33,720 --> 00:20:34,720
Tak preto...

319
00:20:34,720 --> 00:20:36,020
Tak preto čo...

320
00:20:36,020 --> 00:20:37,930
No...

321
00:20:37,930 --> 00:20:40,600
To ona ma sem priviedla.

322
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:42,650
Čo, Anju?

323
00:20:49,540 --> 00:20:52,070
Oh, to šteklí. Prestaň s tým.

324
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:54,230
Ohh.. Anju.

325
00:20:54,410 --> 00:20:56,540
Oh, takže...
Hej, Maaka.

326
00:20:56,540 --> 00:20:59,040
Áno? Čo je?

327
00:20:59,480 --> 00:21:01,640
Stalo sa veľa vecí, takže som na to zabudol...

328
00:21:01,750 --> 00:21:04,450
ale, čo sa stane ľuďom, ktorých pohryzieš..oh...

329
00:21:09,660 --> 00:21:11,490
Vyzerá to...

330
00:21:11,730 --> 00:21:14,490
